class.name: StatisticalReferenceDatasetFactory

javadoc.text: A factory to create instances of {@link StatisticalReferenceDataset} from * available resources.
Creates a new buffered reader from the specified resource name.
javadoc.param: name the name of the resource
javadoc.throws: IOException if an I/O error occured

javadoc.text: Returns an array with all available reference datasets.
javadoc.throws: IOException if an I/O error occurs
